description: This pumpkin curry is excellent during this chilly time of the year, where tender pumpkin is scented with a very basic mixture of spices and manages a naturally creamy texture
Delicious crispy Falafel with fresh creamy hummus from a traditional recipe. Served with a selection of dips.
Tastey broccoli on a bed of creamy noodles with local Shitake mushrooms
Curried sausage in a rich tomato sauce with crispy potato slices and a tomato bean side.
Traditional Gnocchi with italian walnut pesto and fresh basil leaves sprinkled on the top.
Traditional Argininian green uncooked sauce made from fresh parsley, oregano, garlic, olive oil, vinegar, and red pepper flake over salad and crispy sliced baked potatoes.
